  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213540/extras/780f331f99cf5aeb80237da39f1b1341.poster.avif?t=1738579374\" width=800 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213540/extras/780f331f99cf5aeb80237da39f1b1341.webm?t=1738579374\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213540/extras/780f331f99cf5aeb80237da39f1b1341.mp4?t=1738579374\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Just Eat The Rich </strong>is a action packed wave based First person shooter, survivor style Game with roguelike elements, you have 20 minutes to kill the rich collect money and redistribute all their wealth to the poor. Play alone or together with a friend!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213540/extras/bba4e2c5792647327a8881a6ef81ba71.poster.avif?t=1738579374\" width=800 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213540/extras/bba4e2c5792647327a8881a6ef81ba71.webm?t=1738579374\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213540/extras/bba4e2c5792647327a8881a6ef81ba71.mp4?t=1738579374\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fight Bosses</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take down the most obnoxious Billionaires by fighting Unique Bosses during your crusade, <br>and bring these arrogant tycoons to their knees in the most outrageous showdowns imaginable!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213540/extras/afed5c5e3d0020b0003facd2eed41f38.poster.avif?t=1738579374\" width=800 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213540/extras/afed5c5e3d0020b0003facd2eed41f38.webm?t=1738579374\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213540/extras/afed5c5e3d0020b0003facd2eed41f38.mp4?t=1738579374\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unlock weapons and skills</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Level up and choose from a number of skills to build the most optimal way off distributing the wealth.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213540/extras/52f777bbf05dd946bd1dd55deaf82105.poster.avif?t=1738579374\" width=800 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213540/extras/52f777bbf05dd946bd1dd55deaf82105.webm?t=1738579374\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213540/extras/52f777bbf05dd946bd1dd55deaf82105.mp4?t=1738579374\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Use the Money</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Reinvest the Funds you acquired Find the spots to buy Stronger Weapons with the Money you collected!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213540/extras/59cced7e93a52c1108710ebe700ef655.poster.avif?t=1738579374\" width=800 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213540/extras/59cced7e93a52c1108710ebe700ef655.webm?t=1738579374\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213540/extras/59cced7e93a52c1108710ebe700ef655.mp4?t=1738579374\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Collect Powerful Weapons</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are other ways to acquire the mot powerful weapons!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213540/extras/54fae7a5ff8933816a1f4c3794120678.poster.avif?t=1738579374\" width=800 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213540/extras/54fae7a5ff8933816a1f4c3794120678.webm?t=1738579374\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213540/extras/54fae7a5ff8933816a1f4c3794120678.mp4?t=1738579374\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Birdman’s Done Waiting</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The politicians failed, so now it’s time to take matters (and money) into your own hands. Arm up, bust into the mansions of the Elites, and Just Eat the Rich!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213540/extras/e8e76325a24c968ff6f4324ec41ccb3d.poster.avif?t=1738579374\" width=800 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213540/extras/e8e76325a24c968ff6f4324ec41ccb3d.webm?t=1738579374\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213540/extras/e8e76325a24c968ff6f4324ec41ccb3d.mp4?t=1738579374\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features</strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as Birdman </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buy weapons </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >level up </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >choose Skills </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Secret Upgrade combinations </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Redistribute the Wealth </p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213540/extras/780f331f99cf5aeb80237da39f1b1341.poster.avif?t=1738579374\" width=800 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213540/extras/780f331f99cf5aeb80237da39f1b1341.webm?t=1738579374\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213540/extras/780f331f99cf5aeb80237da39f1b1341.mp4?t=1738579374\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Just Eat The Rich </strong>is a action packed wave based First person shooter, survivor style Game with roguelike elements, you have 20 minutes to kill the rich collect money and redistribute all their wealth to the poor. Play alone or together with a friend!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213540/extras/bba4e2c5792647327a8881a6ef81ba71.poster.avif?t=1738579374\" width=800 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213540/extras/bba4e2c5792647327a8881a6ef81ba71.webm?t=1738579374\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213540/extras/bba4e2c5792647327a8881a6ef81ba71.mp4?t=1738579374\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fight Bosses</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take down the most obnoxious Billionaires by fighting Unique Bosses during your crusade, <br>and bring these arrogant tycoons to their knees in the most outrageous showdowns imaginable!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"b